lt="Vitalik 解釋轉移 ETH ：2018 年起就不再為個人利益賣幣" width="600" height="288" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vitalik-解釋轉移-ETH-：2018-年起就不再為個人利益賣幣.png?resize=600%2C288&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vitalik-解釋轉移-ETH-：2018-年起就不再為個人利益賣幣.png?resize=300%2C144&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vitalik-解釋轉移-ETH-：2018-年起就不再為個人利益賣幣.png?resize=1024%2C491&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vitalik-解釋轉移-ETH-：2018-年起就不再為個人利益賣幣.png?resize=768%2C368&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Vitalik-解釋轉移-ETH-：2018-年起就不再為個人利益賣幣.png?w=1206&amp;ssl=1 1206w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-recalc-dims="1" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><h2><span class="ez-toc-section" id="Vitalik_%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E5%B7%B2%E8%B3%A3%E5%87%BA_83_%E8%90%AC%E6%9E%9A_ETH"></span>Vitalik 地址已賣出 83 萬枚 ETH<span class="ez-toc-section-end"></span></h2><p>Vitalik 相關地址從過去至今的賣出與均價為：</p><p><img class="alignnone wp-image-81016 size-full" src="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2023-10-18-%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8811.42.24.png?resize=1878%2C1158&amp;ssl=1" alt="vitalik pnl" width="1878" height="1158" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截圖-2023-10-18-上午 11.42.24.png?w=1878&amp;ssl=1 1878w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截圖-2023-10-18-上午 11.42.24.png?resize=300%2C185&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截圖-2023-10-18-上午 11.42.24.png?resize=1024%2C631&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截圖-2023-10-18-上午 11.42.24.png?resize=600%2C370&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截圖-2023-10-18-上午 11.42.24.png?resize=768%2C474&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/abmedia.io/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/截圖-2023-10-18-上午 11.42.24.png?resize=1536%2C947&amp;ssl=1 1536w" size