        <item>
            <title>
                <![CDATA[檢察官提新證據：FTX 在英雄聯盟、著名音樂節贊助近兩億美元]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="intro_quote">聯邦檢察官在 SBF 案中完整地發佈了 FTX 在加密貨幣牛市期間簽署的數十項贊助協議，試圖以此證明 SBF 一系列災難性的財務決策和魯莽支出。</p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_56_1 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">內容目錄</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/ftx-agreed-to-pay-riot-games-and-tomorrowland#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-652fe022220a4"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
